<Paragraph>
Essential XlsIO is a library that is used to create Excel workbooks without being dependent on Microsoft Excel.
</Paragraph>

<Paragraph>
This category contains the samples that demonstrate the creation of a spreadsheet from scratch and reading the values from an existing spreadsheet.Here is a list of samples with description.
</Paragraph>

<List>
<ListItem><Paragraph><Bold>Create Spreadsheet</Bold> - This sample demonstrates how a simple spreadsheet can be created from scratch.</Paragraph></ListItem>
<ListItem><Paragraph><Bold>Find and Extract</Bold> - This sample demonstrates XlsIO's capability of reading cell values and displaying a cell's text from an existing worksheet.</Paragraph></ListItem>
</List>
